T1  - Note—A Simple Edge Elimination Criterion in a Search for the Center of a Graph
AU  - Halpern, Jonathan
Y1  - 1979/01/01
PY  - 1979
DA  - 1979/01/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.25.1.105
